{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_11_01_short",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜 1話 どういたしまして (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ある日のライブ後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――After a live performance one day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 11566.666666699999,
          "startTime": 11.5666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様。みんな、この後は別の仕事があるのよね\n大変だと思うけど頑張ってね。それじゃ、また後で",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work everyone. You all have other jobs after this‚ right?\nI think it'll be tough‚ but do your best. See you later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.033333381
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ……今日のステージは、イメージ通りに出来た\n月ストとの里帰りライブに向けての準備も順調",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew… today's stage went exactly as I imagined.\nThe preparations for the homecoming live with Moon Tempest are going smoothly too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "これもスタッフのみなさんが支えてくれるおかげよね\n特に、{user}さんには感謝しないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is all thanks to the support from all the staff.\nEspecially {user}-san‚ I need to thank him.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.7666695118
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "今日はこの後オフだし、そろそろ帰ろうっと\nって……あれ、{user}さん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm off after this today‚ so I should head home soon.\nWait… oh‚ {user}-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.1000027974,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.1000027974
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.9000028451
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "まいったな、スケジュール的に絶対無理だが……\n星見市での久しぶりのライブだし無下に断る訳にも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is trouble‚ it's absolutely impossible schedule-wise…\nBut it's a live in Hoshimi City after so long‚ so I can't just refuse…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.5333361308,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.5000028451
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.5000028451,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livecorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livecorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.1666695118
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "うわっ！？　な、なんだ怜か。驚いた\n今日のステージ、凄く良かったよ。お疲れ様",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoa!? O-oh‚ it's Rei. You startled me.\nToday's stage was really good. Good work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.8333361308,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_11_01-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます。……じゃなくて\n何を悩んでるんですか？　口から悩みがもれてましたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you. …But that's not the point.\nWhat are you worrying about? You were saying your worries out loud.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.1666694641,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}